N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 86.1 - General requirements

State Regulations

Each exhibit shall contain: (a) a title page showing: (1)
the applicant's name; (2)
the title of the exhibit; and
(3)
the proper designation of the exhibit; and
(b) if consisting of
10 or more pages, a table of contents citing, by page and section number or
subdivision, the component elements or matters contained in the
exhibit. Notes
